<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const takeWhile = (arr, func) => {
  for (let i of arr.keys()) if (func(arr[i])) return arr.slice(0, i);
  return arr;
};]]></content>
	<description>Removes elements in an array until the passed function returns `true`. Returns the removed elements.  Loop through the array, using a `for...of` loop over `Array.keys()` until the returned value from the function is `true`. Return the removed elements, using `Array.slice()`.</description>
